data.description: Come see this wonderful home that sits on 2 acres of land.  The home features 3 beds, 3 baths, a wonderful large kitchen that overlooks the dining and living room. Outside there is an beautiful freeform diving pool with spa and huge patio perfect for entertaining. Inside the house you will find large bedrooms, spacious bathrooms and closets, granite countertops, lots of dimmable lights and a huge family room with lots of windows overlooking the majestic back yard. The house also has a full wired security camera system. There is also a huge 1500 square foot steel building with an apartment inside it and still has storage for your tools and toys. The entire back yard is fenced in and the majority of the front yard is also fenced.  The house runs on city water, but also has a well to irrigate the entire yard.  The roof, gutters and leaf guards were replaced in 2021 and the house was also repainted in 2021.
